    Used for BOTH creating a new mask (launched from btnAddMask in CreatorHomeActivity)
    and editing an existing one (launched from btnEdit in CreatorItemCardActivity).
    When editing, pre-fill all fields using the MASK_ID extra passed via Intent.

    STRUCTURE:
    - Top bar         : hamburger menu (left) + username (center)
    - Name card       : editable mask name
    - Photos card     : 5 rows (Main + First–Fourth), each with thumbnail + label + pick button
                        Each slot supports both image and video via ActivityResultLauncher
    - Tags card       : chip group showing added tags + text input to add new ones
    - Save button     : saves new or updated mask to DB

